9
00:02:59,546 --> 00:03:02,646
It cannot be done without him.
And it will be done.

10
00:03:03,250 --> 00:03:05,590
Exactly as I said.

11
00:03:06,386 --> 00:03:09,576
-l will not disappoint you, my Lord.
-Good.

12
