these past few months, Wormtail.

1307
02:05:01,794 --> 02:05:03,844
Thank you, master.

1308
02:05:04,731 --> 02:05:06,251
Thank you.

1309
02:05:09,569 --> 02:05:11,649
-Such a handsome boy.
-Don't touch him!

1310
02:05:13,406 --> 02:05:14,716
Harry.

1311
02:05:15,074 --> 02:05:17,534
I'd almost forgotten you were here.

1312
02:05:18,044 --> 02:05:21,914
Standing on the bones
of my father. Yeah.

1313
02:05:22,615 --> 02:05:23,815
I'd introduce you...

1314
02:05:24,150 --> 02:05:27,929
...but word has it you're almost
as famous as me these days.

1315
02:05:31,124 --> 02:05:33,464
The boy who lived.

1316
02:05:33,960 --> 02:05:36,510
How lies have fed your legend, Harry.

1317
02:05:37,030 --> 02:05:40,540
Shall l reveal what really happened
that night 13 years ago?

1318
02:05:41,200 --> 02:05:45,360
Shall I divulge how
I truly lost my powers?

1319
02:05:46,105 --> 02:05:47,504
Yes, shall 1?

1320
02:05:48,041 --> 02:05:49,211
It was love.

1321
02:05:49,542 --> 02:05:53,492
You see, when dear, sweet Lily Potter
gave her life for her only son...

1322
02:05:54,213 --> 02:05:56,492
...she provided the ultimate protection.

1323
02:05:57,216 --> 02:05:58,796
I could not touch him.

1324
02:06:00,253 --> 02:06:02,123
It was old magic.

1325
02:06:02,555 --> 02:06:04,545
Something I should have foreseen.

1326
02:06:04,991 --> 02:06:06,571
But no matter, no matter.

1327
02:06:06,959 --> 02:06:08,889
Things have changed.

1328
02:06:09,929 --> 02:06:12,999
l can touch you...

1329
02:06:14,033 --> 02:06:15,553
. NOW.

1330
02:06:23,910 --> 02:06:25,080
Yeah.

1331
02:06:31,584 --> 02:06:34,834
Astonishing what a few drops
of your blood will do, eh, Harry?

1332
02:06:36,422 --> 02:06:37,942
Pick up your wand, Potter.

1333
02:06:39,759 --> 02:06:41,719
I said, pick it up! Get up! Get up!

1334
02:06:43,563 --> 02:06:45,613
You've been taught how to duel,
I presume, yes?

1335
02:06:46,065 --> 02:06:48,205
First, we bow to each other.

1336
02:06:48,668 --> 02:06:50,748
Come on, now, Harry.
The niceties must be observed.

1337
02:06:51,204 --> 02:06:54,044
Dumbledore wouldn't want you
to forget your manners, would he?

1338
02:06:54,607 --> 02:06:55,777
I said, bow.

1339
02:06:57,810 --> 02:07:01,620
-That’s better. And now....
-No.

1340
02:07:02,548 --> 02:07:04,188
Crucio!

1341
02:07:06,886 --> 02:07:08,406
Crucio!

1342
02:07:09,689 --> 02:07:11,389
Attaboy, Harry.

1343
02:07:11,791 --> 02:07:13,661
Your parents would be proud.

1344
02:07:14,227 --> 02:07:17,217
Especially your filthy Muggle mother.

1345
02:07:17,797 --> 02:07:19,196
Expelliar--

1346
02:07:22,401 --> 02:07:24,510
I'm going to kill you, Harry Potter.

1347
02:07:24,971 --> 02:07:26,721
I'm going to destroy you.

1348
02:07:29,175 --> 02:07:34,065
After tonight, no one will ever again
question my powers.

1349
02:07:35,381 --> 02:07:37,631
After tonight, if they speak of you...

1350
02:07:38,117 --> 02:07:40,457
...they'll speak only of how you...

1351
02:07:41,087 --> 02:07:42,697
...begged for death.

1352
02:07:43,089 --> 02:07:46,399
And I, being a merciful Lord...

1353
02:07:47,393 --> 02:07:48,793
...obliged.

1354
02:07:49,328 --> 02:07:50,638
Get up!

1355
02:07:55,835 --> 02:07:57,565
Don't you turn your back on me,
Harry Potter!

1356
02:07:57,970 --> 02:07:59,960
l want you to look at me
when I kill you!

1357
02:08:00,406 --> 02:08:03,216
I want to see the light
leave your eyes!

1358
02:08:17,557 --> 02:08:19,077
Have it your way.

1359
02:08:20,326 --> 02:08:22,436
-Expelliarmus!
-Avada Kedavra!

1360
02:08:40,246 --> 02:08:42,586
Do nothing! He’s mine to finish!

1361
02:08:47,486 --> 02:08:48,976
He’s mine!

1362
02:09:22,255 --> 02:09:25,765
Harry, when the connection is broken,
you must get to the Portkey.

1363
02:09:26,425 --> 02:09:28,235
We can linger for a moment
to give you some time...

1364
02:09:28,661 --> 02:09:30,211
...but only a moment.
Do you understand?

1365
02:09:31,631 --> 02:09:34,291
Harry, take my body back, will you?

1366
02:09:34,834 --> 02:09:37,054
Take my body back to my father.

1367
02:09:38,404 --> 02:09:39,574
Let go.

1368
02:09:40,206 --> 02:09:41,936
Sweetheart, you're ready.

1369
02:09:43,009 --> 02:09:45,319
Let go! Let go!

1370
02:09:51,384 --> 02:09:52,584
Acciof

1371
02:09:58,457 --> 02:10:00,207
No!

1372
02:10:13,205 --> 02:10:14,605
He did it!

1373
02:10:16,042 --> 02:10:17,502
Harry!

1374
02:10:20,479 --> 02:10:21,789
Harry!

1375
02:10:23,182 --> 02:10:26,022
No! No! No, don't!

1376
02:10:26,719 --> 02:10:28,359
For God’s sake, Dumbledore,
