1377
02:10:28,888 --> 02:10:31,138
He's back. He’s back.

1378
02:10:31,624 --> 02:10:33,404
Voldemort's back.

1379
02:10:33,826 --> 02:10:35,936
Cedric, he asked me
to bring his body back.

1380
02:10:36,395 --> 02:10:38,445
I couldn’t leave him, not there.

1381
02:10:38,898 --> 02:10:41,358
It’s all right, Harry. It’s all right.

1382
02:10:41,867 --> 02:10:43,887
He’s home. You both are.

1383
02:10:44,337 --> 02:10:47,527
Keep everybody in their seats.
A boy has just been killed.

1384
02:10:51,043 --> 02:10:54,263
